definitions.definition: A pintail duck , a type of dabbling duck with a characteristic pointed tail.

subdefinitions.definition: A northern pintail , Anas acuta , a dabbling duck of the northern hemisphere that has a long pointed tail.

definitions.definition: Any of various species of libellulid dragonfly of the genus Acisoma , endemic to Africa and Asia.
The end of a fastening pin or mandrel on a Huckbolt or pop rivet that is broken off when installation is complete.
A surfboard with a pointed back end.
